Android Tegra 250 mozilla-inbound opt test reftest-1 on 2011/06/29 16:35:18 

This test compares the dash rendering of <canvas> with SVG.  It failed in this test run apparently because the test and reference were positioned very slightly differently (at least, that's my best guess).

The results of android reftests didn't appear on my tryserver run, and I can't reproduce this failure with desktop reftest-ipc (note this test *doesn't* run as part of RIPC; I can't repro when I manually run reftest-ipc), and the android reftest results are few and far between on tinderbox so it's not easy to diagnose this problem.  I will sadly random-if(Android) this test for now.
